inquiries.query:
/*
In the job postings fact table get the job id, job title short, Job location, job via, and salary year avg columns. 
Only look at jobs that are not 'Part-time' jobs (hint: look at the job schedule_type column).

*/

SELECT
	job_id,
    job_title_short,
    job_location,
    job_via,
    salary_year_avg
	
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
where
	job_schedule_type <> 'part-time'
inquiries.name: com practice problem-3
